
## ✅ Day 20 – Sum of digits

**File name:** `day20-sum-of-digits.java`

```java
public class Day20SumOfDigits {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int n = 12345;
        int sum = 0;

        int temp = n;
        while (temp > 0) {
            int digit = temp % 10;
            sum += digit;
            temp /= 10;
        }

        System.out.println("Number: " + n);
        System.out.println("Sum of digits = " + sum);
    }
}
